00:20:33.788 --> 00:20:36.001
Aku dah cakap jangan datang.

196
00:20:41.373 --> 00:20:44.066
Aku dah cakap jangan datang...

197
00:20:48.993 --> 00:20:51.092
sejak hujan.

198
00:20:54.393 --> 00:20:56.506
Sejak hujan.

199
00:20:57.426 --> 00:21:00.339
Aku dah cakap jangan datang.

200
00:21:11.259 --> 00:21:13.656
Bukan salah awak.

201
00:21:16.330 --> 00:21:18.216
Bukan salah awak.

202
00:21:19.803 --> 00:21:21.262
jangan menangis.

203
00:21:21.262 --> 00:21:23.369
Jangan menangis, Jun Kyung.

204
